"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-02-07-herbert-morrisons-daley-eyes-olympic-berth\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IF his confidence is anything to go by, Herbert Morrison's Deandre Daley will be making some noise - not only at the junior level but he could also do so at the seniors as he eyes a spot on the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 40, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Morrison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1336798392000628e-18, \"text\": \"Herbert Morrison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Morrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Morrison\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, who turns 19 years old on Thursday, opened his season in the 400m at the Youngster Goldsmith Meet, and he is oozing with confidence.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Based on how the season progresses, if I am in that shape I will definitely go for it,\\\" Daley told theJamaica Observerafter struggling to catch his breath following a gruelling 400m run.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete was asked if he believes he can realistically qualify for Paris seeing that Jamaica has quality 100m runners vying for only six spots.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999598986586, \"rank\": 4.0101360481119526e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999901318838378, \"rank\": 9.866175077005846e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley would have to get by Oblique Seville, Ackeem Blake, Rohan Watson, Yohan Blake, and other promising sprinters.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999998811952153, \"rank\": 1.0981681261083937e-07, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}, {\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9972510999066259, \"rank\": 0.002756376536677969, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\"}, {\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Dragon_Prince\", \"score\": 0.9834615831480698, \"rank\": 0.016816398539546012, \"text\": \"Rohan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Dragon_Prince\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Dragon_Prince\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dr._Watson\", \"score\": 0.9095491874356758, \"rank\": 0.07156014738475307, \"text\": \"Watson\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dr._Watson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dr._Watson\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yohan Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not worried about the competition.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am out there to do my own damage,\\\" Daley said.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley has a personal best of 10.08 seconds and was the second-fastest junior athlete behind Bouwahjgie Nkrumie, who became the first schoolboy to go below the 10-second barrier with 9.98s.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley looked sharp and strong in his 400m, holding a lead down the backstretch, but was caught close to home by Roshane Symister of Jamaica College (JC) who finished in 48.69s.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_College\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, who said he felt stronger than last season, clocked a personal best 50.44s and was 17th overall.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today's race was mainly for training for the 100m further down,\\\" Daley said.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fans are expecting great things so that's all [what's] left to do, show them great things.\\\"\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for his attempt at the 100m record during which he finished second last year in 10.14, he said, \\\"Only time can tell.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the work is being put in, then I am pleased with any time I run.\\\"\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hector Benjamin is a challenger to Daley, and the JC athlete's coach said last week that he can set the record after opening his 100m with 10.36s.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hector\", \"score\": 0.9999999999683951, \"rank\": 2.1375765851550762e-11, \"text\": \"Hector\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hector\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hector\"}, {\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.9914503471916911, \"rank\": 0.0083364748581384, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}, {\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Cycle\", \"score\": 0.9824357233106699, \"rank\": 0.0172537383663654, \"text\": \"JC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Cycle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Cycle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Benjamin is to get the record he will have to go through Daley first, and that will be no easy feat.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.9914503471916911, \"rank\": 0.0083364748581384, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": []}]}"